                <br>
                <br>
                I started this website largely out of surprise and frustration that there wasn't anywhere I could go and play with a cryptocurrency in a practical way, without spending real money. There are plenty of videos and online training courses, and the bitcoin "testnet" allows you to download test coins to a wallet, but that is quite a high technical bar for the average person and lacks a co-ordinated flow that takes you through receiving coins and performing transactions.
                <br>
